oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Joelton Grammar School graduation class, 1925
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: A photograph of the 1925 graduation class of Joelton Grammar School, Joelton, Tennessee. The verso notation cites the name of W. Ross McGehee and the typed index card cites: "W. Ross McGhee, one of pupils." Joelton is located primarily in the northwestern portion of Davidson County, with parts of Joelton within Cheatham County. Forms part of the Nashville Room Historic Photographs Collection. 1 photograph : sepia ; 8 x 10 in.
